apons, all physics-based objects you can realistically wield.<br>Features:<br>- Dismember Zombies<br>- Full campaign with story-driven gameplay <br>- Manual and automatic  Reloading System<br>- both hands support<br>- Throw your weapons and kill zombies<br>- Slowmotion <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835530/extras/e46e2860eccb4ab23a0f3cbd1ca23b41.poster.avif?t=1771910185\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835530/extras/e46e2860eccb4ab23a0f3cbd1ca23b41.webm?t=1771910185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835530/extras/e46e2860eccb4ab23a0f3cbd1ca23b41.mp4?t=1771910185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>DIFFERENT TYPES OF GUNS AND WEAPONS TO KILL ZOMBIES. The ambiance of levels will make you afraid and look constantly around. Convenient controls, realistic weapon behavior, and physics will not leave you apathetic, you want to hit the enemy with the butt of your weapon, no problem, do it and finish the zombie while it lies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835530/extras/50d533f0116263329c6339c12397f44d.poster.avif?t=1771910185\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835530/extras/50d533f0116263329c6339c12397f44d.webm?t=1771910185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835530/extras/50d533f0116263329c6339c12397f44d.mp4?t=1771910185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A variety of behavior of zombies will pleasantly surprise and scare you, Try to aim for head-to-kill zombies instantly. Good Luck<br><span class=\"